'''Ibeldisen''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: ''Gastropoda'') d [[asmil (tasnudert)|asmil]] meqqren yakk deg [[astirf (tasnudert)|wadur]] n [[Tigri|tigritin]] acku dges azal n 80% n [[talmest|telmas]] yeṭṭafaren adur-a, akken daɣen i tga d tafesna tameqrant tis snat yakk deg [[aɣersiw|tgelda taɣersawt]] anda i llant dges wazal n 65000 n telmas gar-asent [[aɣlal]] d [[Amillus|umillus]] d [[tazɣurt|tezɣurt]] 

Azal ameqran n ibeldisen lan (sɛan) [[ajeɣlal]] amyiwen ddurayen yis, ijeɣlalen-a ttilin d ubrinen <br/>
Ibeldisen ttidiren deg waṭas n twennaṭin n umadal, Amur ameqran degsen deg waman anda ugar n 3000 n telmas n ibeldisen ttidiren s ddaw n waman n [[ilel|illan]] d [[agaraw|igarawen]] yakk d 5000 n telmas n idem ttidiren deg [[aman iẓidanen|waman iẓidanen]] ([[asif|isafen]], [[iɣzeṛ|iɣezṛawen]], [[agelmim|igelmimen]]) ma d tilmas id yegran ttidirent sufel n tegnit (lqaɛa), Azal ameqran n ibeldisen tetten [[imɣan]] akken i llant telmas tettent isugar igemnawen akken daɣen i llant kra n telma d [[timseksumin]] yerna gant d [[uɣes|timuɣas]]

== Agar, tasensartut d usru ==
